emitism and the collapse of the central state. Kopstein and Wittenberg shed new light on the sources of mass ethnic violence and the ways in which such gruesome acts might be avoided.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aAntisemitismzPolandxHistoryy20th century. 0aHolocaust, Jewish (1939-1945)zEurope, Eastern. 0aHolocaust, Jewish (1939-1945)zPoland. 0aJewsxPersecutionszPolandxHistoryy20th century. 0aPogromszPolandxHistoryy20th century. 4aEurope. 4aHistory. 4aJewish Studies. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Eastern.2bisacsh  aPoland, Ukraine, antisemitism, nationalism, World War II.1 aWittenberg, Jason, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2018z978311060655308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishz978311060425208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2018 Englishz978311060403008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2018z9783110603149oZDB-23-DEG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781501715273?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501715273423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501715273/original  a978-3-11-060403-0  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060425-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060655-3  Cornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2018 